last_episode_to_air.overview: An idol group called "Live un veil" has been formed. The members are Nagisa, Nanami and Kaede, and a tour with fans to the southern island has been announced. All TV and magazines took it and many fans joined. The approved character is Ryou. One day, he received a gift, which contained films, envelopes and some exclusive swimwear for girls. "What is that !?" He opened the envelope, and found tickets to the tour and a letter. He said, "If you take photos using this movie, their libido will be out of control ..."
